14:11.226 --> 14:15.981
Well, it certainly seems to be
a wise and prudent plan, my dear.

14:16.065 --> 14:17.066
It is good.

14:17.232 --> 14:18.984
Phooey! Plan okay.

14:19.193 --> 14:20.903
