14:30.829 --> 14:31.830
<i>Da.</i>

14:31.914 --> 14:33.207
Good. Let's get to work.

14:33.499 --> 14:35.959
"Am," you head up the road
and hide in the trees.

14:36.085 --> 14:38.545
